{"tid":1876550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買唔到口罩係唔開心 但可唔可以唔好大大大力咁屌眾志","createTime":"2020-02-12T12:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:00:26.000Z","uid":314521,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28fa709f3397eea5921d093f1baf06a2331828fd","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"明白大家都好想買口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而見到眾志有口罩都個個即刻衝去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係口罩就得10萬盒 咁就算每個人一盒最後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都一定有人買唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n係屌眾志網上安排大家買之前 可唔可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諗一諗呢個濕鳩政府有冇幫過香港人買呢啲物品先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n明白當中可能都有巴絲俾Bot搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嬲都正常嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係你而家點屌眾志 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">眾志都唔會無啦啦變幾萬盒口罩出黎俾香港市民架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以 點解我地反而唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝眾志</span></span> 而係大大力咁屌鳩佢地先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多咪俾多啲建議佢地 等下次大家都有公平嘅機會買到口罩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我愛眾志 多謝你地!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9a8348fe989c5c39a96f865d1c89b45df68ffb5a","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"我愛眾志"},{"pid":"07ec33128139be9e0615b080b6e14430cf6c2c15","tid":1876550,"uid":94978,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"2000盒咋🤔"},{"pid":"b78be592f6636e6d723bb5f1543a0369aa2bda90","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"推俾大家記住眾志係幫大家嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9caef01ab2aa346c25938949e635a663d64895b","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07ec33128139be9e0615b080b6e14430cf6c2c15","tid":1876550,"uid":94978,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"2000盒咋🤔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"我無買 留俾其他俾我更加少嘅人買 真係得咁少咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09500d75729073534a096d22f478f3e0635126c9","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"P推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b59819a197967fa30b500331a2cd31b38c36ede","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"推唔到就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c88ef5d454a2dd32206b97bc89a44ee2c33e0f","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eea1432e3b3463c91669c1747ae8e7d3998387a","tid":1876550,"uid":314521,"like":0,"dislike"